comments: Easy, read the book, easy tests. Cool class, lots of discussion. She tries to make it fun. No essays, one project, a few journal entries, 4 easy tests. Jamie is super nice/understanding.

She is a very straight forward teacher. She lectures, discusses, and then we are tested on what was taught. She posts study guides with exactly what is on the test. I am not a COM major and I enjoyed this class. It was fairly easy and not a lot of work.
